SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Ontario
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO (1) the Hon. KATHRYN N. FELDMAN from June 1 to 6, 2014, inclusive; (2) the Hon. PETER D. ALEXANDRA HOY from June 12 to 17, 2014, inclusive; (5) the Hon. ROBERT J. SHARPE from June 21 and 22, 2014, inclusive.
